values:
Empty spaces, fill me up with holes

Distant faces, with no place left to go

without you, within me, i can't find the way

where im going, was anybodys game

i tired to go on like i never knew you

im awake but my world is half a sleep

i pray for this heart to be unbroken

but without you all im going to be is incomplete

vioces tell me i should carry on

but i am swimming in an ocean all alone

baby, my baby its written on your face

you still wonder if we made a big mistake

i tried to go like i never knew you

i'm awake but my world is half asleep

i pray for this heart to be unbroken

but without you all im going to be is incomplete

i dont mean to drag it on

but i cant seem to let you go

i dont want to make you face this world alone

I've decided to stop with the dumb "sappy entries".  I've noticed that all I do is complain, so I'm going to stop doing that.  Just a thought.

So I've also decided that everyone needs to stop freaking out about their weight and eating "right" (whatever that is anymore).   Okay, so I am TOTALLY contradicting myself here, but thats something I'm going to try to stop doing myself.  I need to stop complaining about my body so mcuh and just deal with it!!!  So if I ever complain to any of you, just slap me around a bit. I'm sure you guys, my friends, don't like to constantly listen to me complain about my body, so I'm going to stop doing that.  Oh yes, and an addition to that, I'm going to stop talking about what I eat.  I've noticed I do that a lot, and I'm sure you guys DON'T CARE about what I eat. So I'm stopping doing that too!!! :) So if you hear my do any of this...please TELL ME TO SHUT UP! I'll understand! :P

Thanks!

So for some reason, I thought I have already updated since V-day, but apparently not...how weird. Oh well.  So lately nothing special has been going on. I'm still out of vball and gym class. Woo to the gym, but boo *thumbs down* to the vball.  Its feeling much better thou! I'm getting there! I'm really nervous about softball tryouts though because those are next Monday, and I'm not sure if I'll be able to come back to gym. I'm nervous about that. :/ Well have to see what goes down.

So I got a parking sticker! How wicked is that? :) I'm excited, but if I don't get my grades up my dad isn't going to let me drive :( YIKES. I'm scared about that. Damn school. Oh well, I'll work on it.

I really don't have anything to write about because I'm not a very interesting person.  But I really can't wait until the summer...I need to find myself a boy...I really don't understand my situation...maybe you can help. So pretty much...my situation is...guys aren't interested...I'm...just..."attractice"...I guess....:/ This is so lame, I feel so stupid! Guys in school are dumb, its not even like there are guys at school that I'm interested in, they are all pretty much a bunch of jackasses, there are a few exceptions though. I NEED TO MEET SOME NEW BOYS FROM DIFFERENT SCHOOLS!!!.....

But enough of my complaining about stupid things....I'm outta here! Take care!

:)

OoOOOoOO look I'm spirited! Look at that color! :P 

Today, the average Valentines Day! Nothing special. I had no one to share it w/, which is no surprise. :P  Doesnt bother me thou, I havent had someone to share vday w/ ever before so I wouldnt know what its like, so i have NOTHING to miss! :) SO its cool!!  I did get a few valentines, wahoo I'm loved :P!

The ankle is getting better. It is still pretty colors, but doesnt hurt as bad to walk on it, but i'm still wearing this HIDIOUS boot! haha, oh well, as long as im better before like the 27th or so. i have softball tryouts and our first qualifier is right around that time too!!!!!! so all i gotta say is that my doctor releases me sooner than im out of gym for! 3 weeks! thats a long ass time!

I gave up cookies/candy/brownies/desserts for lent! Its going to be tough!

Oh well, enough of my complaining! :P I'll catch ya'll later!

Call me! We'll do lunch ;)

Hello there.  So it seems like its been a while since I've updated this thingy.  Oh well, you don't want to hear about my uneventful days anyways, so I guess its a good thing.  But I do have a story to tell you today.  Yesterday at practice I landed on top of a ball and rolled my ankle. YUCK, I know right.  So I stayed home from school today seeing as I couldn't walk on it, I went and saw a doctor.  He told me "severe sprain" and that I could possibly be out for like a month, AT THE MOST!  That is a little extreme for just a sprained ankle.  Probably like a week or two, two at most. We'll see how well it heals. :)  I'm going to miss a tourney this weekend :( Go figure.  But now I have a softcast on my foot for a week and I also have to wear this HUGE boot so that I don't move it.  Oh yeah, and did I mention I get to walk around school w/ crutches! NOOO! I'm going to hate it! YUCK!  People babying me and such, I hate it.  None of that!  Oh well its only tomorrow and Friday, and hopefully I'll be alright for next week. :)

But thats my story for you.  Nothing too exciting, kind of lame actually, but oh well. :)

 

Ben Folds_Fred Jones Pt 2

Fred sits alone at his desk in the dark

theres an akward young shadow that waits in the hall

and hes cleared all his things and hes put them in boxes

things that remind him life has been good

25 years hes worked at the paper

a mans here to take him downstairs

and i'm sorry mr. jones its time
